  "category": "Uncategorized",
  "description": "Align Footer Navigation Menu with Header Menu\n\nCreate a footer navigation menu that mirrors the top-level items from the header menu, ensuring consistent structure and alignment across both navigation areas.\n\nRequirements:\n- Extract top-level menu items from the existing header navigation\n- Generate footer menu dynamically using the same data source as header menu\n- Ensure footer menu items match header items in order and content\n- Maintain visual alignment between footer and header menu layouts\n- Verify both menus update automatically when navigation structure changes\n- Apply appropriate styling to distinguish footer menu while maintaining consistency\n- Test that all footer menu links function correctly and point to same destinations as header\n- Handle responsive behavior for both menus on mobile and tablet breakpoints\n- Ensure accessibility features (ARIA labels, keyboard navigation) are consistent between both menus",
  "title": "Add Dynamic Footer Navigation Menu Mirroring Header",
